    <item>
      <title>日本将向美国出售导弹以放宽武器出口规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/japan-to-sell-missiles-to-us-in-relaxation-of-arms-export-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府表示，周五放宽了对武器出口的限制，并正式批准了向美国出口爱国者导弹的计划，满足其盟友的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/japan-to-sell-missiles-to-us-in-relaxation-of-arms-export-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 09:22:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于红海袭击扰乱全球流动，石油将每周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于红海袭击迫使数百艘船只采取更安全但更长的航线，延迟了石油货物的交付，石油价格延续了两个月来的最大单周涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 00:11:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
